summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Nineteenth Avenue Northwest from West 65th Street to West 75th Street in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 18657, creating Local Improvement District No. 1758 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
